"{\"uid\": \"nbcnews.com-tech-internet-olympic-chocolate-muffins-brought-new-york-city-pop-rcna167945\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  news Alerts  There are no new alerts at this time  What would you do for a chocolate muffin?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 94, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what independent designer Kelin Carolyn Zhang asked herself as she watched Norwegian swimmerHenrik Christiansenproclaim his love for the chocolate muffins served in the Olympic Village on TikTok.\", \"from\": 96, \"to\": 298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 135, \"end\": 142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carolyn_Culliton\", \"score\": 0.6788141084267296, \"rank\": 0.398102982694321, \"text\": \"Carolyn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carolyn_Culliton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carolyn_Culliton\"}, {\"begin\": 178, \"end\": 187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9673438319092791, \"rank\": 0.025185371919470474, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}, {\"begin\": 272, \"end\": 287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999998940439, \"rank\": 7.196137987971602e-11, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 291, \"end\": 297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.425814375538011e-33, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Christiansen posted over a dozen videos about his beloved \\\"choccy muffin,\\\" and Olympic stars like \\\"Pommel horse guy\\\"Stephen Nedoroscikand track and field gold medalistGabby Thomasalso shared their love for the baked good.\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 521, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zhang was intrigued.\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 543, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Three weeks later, she tracked down the French supplier, facilitated a shipment of muffins to the U.S. and dealt with the resulting challenges, all to bring the viral muffins to New York City for a pop-up event.\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 585, \"end\": 591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9931296762082216, \"rank\": 0.0061850046518728335, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 723, \"end\": 736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999999804459, \"rank\": 1.9628050870721125e-11, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a thread on X, Zhangdetailedhow she worked with New York City cafeIsshiki Matchato bring the viral muffins to hundreds of New Yorkers on Aug. 17.\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 808, \"end\": 821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999999804459, \"rank\": 1.9628050870721125e-11, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a big believer in just trying new things,\\\" Zhang told NBC News.\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 967, \"end\": 975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"score\": 0.9998772908744664, \"rank\": 7.019987390734022e-05, \"text\": \"NBC News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think this was one of the more extreme examples of that.\\\"\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1037, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her viral quest for the muffins began: she produced and posted several videos trying to identify the creator of the muffins.\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She eventuallydiscoveredthat they were made by Coup de pates.\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Around then, a stranger commented that her friend Angel Zheng, the owner of Isshiki Matcha, would be willing to help her import and sell the muffins.\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1282, \"end\": 1287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"score\": 0.9312262122290393, \"rank\": 0.05982733975055392, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\"}, {\"begin\": 1302, \"end\": 1309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\", \"score\": 0.9999997383079404, \"rank\": 2.402909493959567e-07, \"text\": \"Isshiki\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\"}, {\"begin\": 1310, \"end\": 1316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matcha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matcha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matcha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matcha\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think I am the only crazy cafe owner in New York City that would agree to such a short amount of time to do something at this capacity,\\\" Zheng said in an interview with NBC News.\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999999804459, \"rank\": 1.9628050870721125e-11, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 1517, \"end\": 1522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"score\": 0.9312262122290393, \"rank\": 0.05982733975055392, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\"}, {\"begin\": 1549, \"end\": 1557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"score\": 0.9998772908744664, \"rank\": 7.019987390734022e-05, \"text\": \"NBC News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Isshiki Matcha, which has been open for four months, primarily sells premium matcha and matcha drinks.\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1560, \"end\": 1567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\", \"score\": 0.9999997383079404, \"rank\": 2.402909493959567e-07, \"text\": \"Isshiki\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\"}, {\"begin\": 1568, \"end\": 1574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matcha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matcha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matcha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matcha\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zheng described her interest in bringing authentic food to bigger audiences and doing events like the collaboration with Zhang or fashion pop-ups.\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1809, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1663, \"end\": 1668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"score\": 0.9312262122290393, \"rank\": 0.05982733975055392, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In her thread, Zhang detailed the obstacles she faced in securing the muffins, including: having to reach out to Coup de pates on multiple platforms, getting customs and FDA approval and worrying about the muffins spoiling.\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 2034, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1981, \"end\": 1984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Food_and_Drug_Administration\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7645371002674936e-27, \"text\": \"FDA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Food_and_Drug_Administration\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Food_and_Drug_Administration\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the muffins arrived in the U.S., the customs broker told Zhang that they could not be delivered the day of because the refrigerated truck was too small.\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2193, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The broker offered to ask the airline to store the muffins in a freezer until the next morning and then eventually was able to deliver the same day.\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2342, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zheng even bought a new freezer to store the muffins.\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2343, \"end\": 2348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"score\": 0.9312262122290393, \"rank\": 0.05982733975055392, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zhang described her mindset throughout as focusing on one problem at a time and being solution-oriented.\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2502, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The day of the event, hundreds of New Yorkerslined upstarting at 6 a.m. to buy a muffin.\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2592, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After eating some themselves and sharing with family and friends, the duo sold the remaining 263 muffins.\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2698, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The cafepricedeach muffin at $10, and Zheng said that most of that went to transport costs and they primarily made money that day when customers bought a matcha alongside the muffin.\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2738, \"end\": 2743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"score\": 0.9312262122290393, \"rank\": 0.05982733975055392, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While some online have criticized the hype over a simple muffin, Zhang said that it was lighthearted fun that allowed fans watching the Olympics from a continent away to feel included.\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 3068, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not be an Olympic athlete,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3115, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could eat this viral muffin that all these Olympic athletes can not stop talking about.\\\"\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3207, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zhang described the muffin as light, moist and not too sweet.\", \"from\": 3209, \"to\": 3270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a fan,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3271, \"to\": 3294, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, she was only able to eat three-quarters of a muffin, mostly for a taste test that she posted online, and hopes to try more.\", \"from\": 3295, \"to\": 3427, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zhang and Zheng are trying to import another batch of muffins to sell (and eat), but nothing has been finalized yet.\", \"from\": 3429, \"to\": 3545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3439, \"end\": 3444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"score\": 0.9312262122290393, \"rank\": 0.05982733975055392, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, what Zhang has cherished the most is the experience.\", \"from\": 3546, \"to\": 3605, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Have fun - life is short,\\\" Zhang said.\", \"from\": 3607, \"to\": 3646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Be a little silly.\\\"\", \"from\": 3647, \"to\": 3667, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Victoria Feng is an intern on the NBC News technology desk.\", \"from\": 3669, \"to\": 3728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3669, \"end\": 3677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queen_Victoria\", \"score\": 0.9999739230323439, \"rank\": 2.2985861661199668e-05, \"text\": \"Victoria\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queen_Victoria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queen_Victoria\"}, {\"begin\": 3703, \"end\": 3711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"score\": 0.9998772908744664, \"rank\": 7.019987390734022e-05, \"text\": \"NBC News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9\\u00a02025 NBCUniversal Media, LLC\", \"from\": 3730, \"to\": 3760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3757, \"end\": 3760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"score\": 0.9999999980541361, \"rank\": 1.945953547014952e-09, \"text\": \"LLC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\"}]}]}"